.TH APKW 1 "April 2026" "APKW" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
apkw \- start the APK Workbench services and GTK interface
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B apkw
[\fB--services\fR]
[\fIui-args\fR...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B apkw
starts the APK Workbench background services and, by default, launches the GTK4 user
interface.
.PP
The command is the packaged entry point for the Debian build and resolves to
the installed launcher under
.IR /usr/lib/apkw/bin/apkw-start .
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --services
Start the gRPC services without launching the GTK UI.
.TP
.BR -h ", " --help
Show the launcher help text and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/apkw/logs
Runtime logs written by the launcher and packaged services.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR apkw-ui (1),
.BR apkw-cli (1)
